1
00:00:33,859 --> 00:00:34,479
Lingfeng,

2
00:00:35,259 --> 00:00:36,759
I can give you

3
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:38,200
the power

4
00:00:38,399 --> 00:00:41,000
and wealth of the world.

5
00:00:41,859 --> 00:00:42,520
But why do you

6
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:44,039
go against me?

7
00:00:44,579 --> 00:00:46,060
Are you like your brother,

8
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:48,140
being enchanted by a woman,

9
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,780
and forgetting your last name?

10
00:00:49,979 --> 00:00:50,479
Is that so?

11
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:52,439
Father,

12
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:54,520
brother,

13
00:00:55,780 --> 00:00:57,500
do you really think I don't know

14
00:00:57,579 --> 00:00:58,820
what happened eight years ago?

15
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,880
I didn't expect

16
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,379
the misunderstanding between us

17
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:07,819
to be so deep.

18
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:09,340
Fine,

19
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,859
it's time to tell you the truth.

20
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:13,359
You

21
00:01:13,859 --> 00:01:15,040
are not an adopted child.

22
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,420
You are the flesh and blood

23
00:01:17,519 --> 00:01:20,379
of me and the Queen Mother.

24
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,019
Back then,

25
00:01:28,599 --> 00:01:29,780
I was a horse washer

26
00:01:29,900 --> 00:01:30,980
at the royal stables.

27
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:32,879
He,

28
00:01:33,939 --> 00:01:35,000
Xie Zhicang,

29
00:01:35,719 --> 00:01:37,359
was just a military officer.

30
00:01:38,819 --> 00:01:40,459
I gave my heart to him,

31
00:01:40,579 --> 00:01:41,620
and we pledged our lives to each other.

32
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:44,180
But he,

33
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,560
when he learned the late Emperor

34
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,439
took notice of me because

35
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,500
I resembled the late Empress,

36
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,659
for the sake of power,

37
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:53,379
he offered me to the late Emperor.

38
00:01:54,939 --> 00:01:55,700
And at that time,

39
00:01:57,099 --> 00:01:58,459
I was already pregnant.

40
00:02:00,859 --> 00:02:02,159
Not long after she gave birth to you,

41
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:03,579
relying on

42
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:05,659
her resemblance to the late Empress,

43
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,300
[while I was away at the border,]

44
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,319
[she seduced the late Emperor.]

45
00:02:10,819 --> 00:02:12,020
[To avoid future troubles,]

46
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:14,360
[she cruelly ordered the nanny]

47
00:02:15,659 --> 00:02:17,580
[to dispose of you.]

48
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:23,719
[I had intended]

49
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,939
[to secretly give you away,]

50
00:02:27,620 --> 00:02:28,360
[hoping you]

51
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,340
[could grow up in the civilian world.]

52
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:32,719
[But years later,]

53
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,120
[Xie Zhicang]

54
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,219
threatened me

55
00:02:37,379 --> 00:02:38,979
with this painting

56
00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:40,259
and the news of his son

57
00:02:41,259 --> 00:02:42,699
to pave his way to power.

58
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,860
Fortunately, the nanny was kind-hearted

59
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,060
and placed you in a monastery.

60
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,620
Eight years ago,

61
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:50,340
the Queen Mother learned of this.

62
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:52,539
Fearful of exposure,

63
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,860
she sent assassins

64
00:02:54,099 --> 00:02:57,000
to silence you and the monks.

65
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,159
I arrived in time

66
00:02:59,699 --> 00:03:01,199
to save you from the assassins

67
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:02,560
and brought you back to the Xie family,

68
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,379
raising you with all my care.

69
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:10,719
What about those 300 soldiers?

70
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,960
And the monks in the temple?

71
00:03:12,139 --> 00:03:13,319
They were innocent.

72
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:16,819
It was their misfortune

73
00:03:17,379 --> 00:03:18,159
to have encountered

74
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,520
the assassins sent by the Queen Mother.

75
00:03:22,379 --> 00:03:23,699
I couldn't risk

76
00:03:23,860 --> 00:03:25,599
leak this information.

77
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:27,319
Otherwise,

78
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,060
if the late Emperor finds out,

79
00:03:31,419 --> 00:03:32,099
how could my son

80
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:35,240
survive in this world?

81
00:03:37,599 --> 00:03:39,580
But I was wrong.

82
00:03:40,539 --> 00:03:41,539
The late Emperor

83
00:03:42,539 --> 00:03:44,439
entrusted me to assist the young Emperor

84
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,500
and protect the empire.

85
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,879
But Xie Zhicang harbors treacherous ambitions

86
00:03:49,139 --> 00:03:50,479
and seeks to overthrow the empire.

87
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,259
Over the years,

88
00:03:52,979 --> 00:03:54,840
I've endured and retreated,

89
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:56,039
hoping

90
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:57,900
to bring about a moment of peace

91
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,240
and stability to the empire.

92
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:01,560
However,

93
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,360
this constant retreat

94
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:08,240
has not only fueled his power,

95
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,740
but also sown the seeds of disaster.

96
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:12,979
Now,

97
00:04:13,699 --> 00:04:16,300
with the young emperor weak and the court depleted,

98
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,360
It's the time to change the emperor.

99
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,040
Lingfeng,

100
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,279
you are

101
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:23,439
the royal blood,

102
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:25,639
and you have the ambition to rule the country.

103
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:28,899
I'm willing to clear the way for you,

104
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:31,240
and put you on the throne,

105
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,160
on the top of all the people.

106
00:04:35,100 --> 00:04:35,660
What do you think?

107
00:04:41,019 --> 00:04:41,720
Your Highness,

108
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:42,740
everything is ready.

109
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:53,040
Tomorrow is your brother's big day.

110
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:56,160
I will give him a grand

111
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,560
and proper farewell.

112
00:04:58,439 --> 00:04:59,939
After his burial,

113
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:03,040
we'll have a heart-to-heart talk.

114
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,639
Until then,

115
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,100
stay here.

116
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,639
Think everything

117
00:05:10,379 --> 00:05:11,620
through.

118
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,319
Your Majesty,

119
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,939
Xie Zhicang is using the orphan of a loyalist

120
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,839
using the last of the loyalists as bait.

121
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,579
I implore Your Majesty to intervene

122
00:05:35,819 --> 00:05:36,579
and save them.

123
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:37,220
And also save

124
00:05:37,220 --> 00:05:38,639
the precarious state of the empire.

125
00:05:40,319 --> 00:05:40,720
But...

126
00:05:41,699 --> 00:05:42,540
I...

127
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:46,720
I am powerless to help.

128
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:47,879
Your Majesty,

129
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,160
you are the mother of the empire.

130
00:05:50,740 --> 00:05:51,620
How can you just stand by

131
00:05:51,699 --> 00:05:53,180
and watch the loyal and righteous die,

132
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,339
while the treacherous run rampant?

133
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,480
Thank you, Your Majesty, for your wisdom.

134
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:03,300
You sent the message in time.

135
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:08,620
Your Majesty,

136
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:23,100
my son thought of you until his last breath.

137
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:25,399
His journey to the underworld

138
00:06:25,439 --> 00:06:26,699
must be lonely.

139
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:27,899
It's just right

140
00:06:28,259 --> 00:06:30,000
for you to perform the ghost wedding,

141
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,860
and be buried with him.

142
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:34,959
Take her!

143
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:35,800
Yes!

144
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,639
Your Majesty!

145
00:06:38,279 --> 00:06:38,980
Your Majesty!

146
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,060
Your Majesty!

147
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,500
- Let me go! - Go!

148
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,220
Your Majesty,

149
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,000
please save them!

150
00:06:50,079 --> 00:06:51,339
I've decided to

151
00:06:52,019 --> 00:06:53,920
Huaiyun should be given a grand burial

152
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,240
with the honors due to a prince.

153
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,680
At that time,

154
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,560
Your Majesty and Your Highness

155
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,160
should preside over it in person

156
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,899
to show the grace of heaven.

157
00:07:19,579 --> 00:07:20,860
[The blood flowing in your veins]

158
00:07:20,980 --> 00:07:22,860
[is indeed royal blood.]

159
00:07:24,759 --> 00:07:25,680
[Little slave,]

160
00:07:26,620 --> 00:07:27,740
[do you miss me?]

161
00:07:29,420 --> 00:07:31,500
[I'll make you the emperor,]

162
00:07:32,500 --> 00:07:34,560
[standing above all.]

163
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,180
[From now on,]

164
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,040
[I'm the master,]

165
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,459
[and you're the slave.]

166
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,740
[Your life is mine,]

167
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,019
[not the God's.]

168
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,879
[An Rao was captured.]

169
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,360
She'll be sacrificed in a ghost marriage.

170
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:13,540
[Xie Huaiyun, son of the late Prince of Lin'an,]

171
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:14,939
[a member of the royal family,]

172
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,500
[a descendant of the imperial clan.]

173
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:20,000
[I sympathize with the Prince of Lin'an's loss of his son,]

174
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,879
[and posthumously grant you the title of Duke,]

175
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:23,800
[with a royal tomb.]

176
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,759
[In recognition of your youth and talent,]

177
00:08:27,139 --> 00:08:28,279
[and in mourning for your lonely spirit,]

178
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,259
[I specially select a virtuous girl]

179
00:08:30,459 --> 00:08:32,240
[to be your ghost bride.]

180
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,679
Thank you, Your Majesty.

181
00:08:44,299 --> 00:08:47,679
Please, father of the bride, drink the wedding wine

182
00:08:48,019 --> 00:08:50,580
to celebrate this perfect union.

183
00:09:24,179 --> 00:09:24,980
My son,

184
00:09:26,379 --> 00:09:27,960
I won't let any of those who harmed you

185
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:32,759
get away with it.

186
00:09:39,379 --> 00:09:41,860
Since this girl meets your approval,

187
00:09:43,580 --> 00:09:45,340
let her join you in the afterlife

188
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,299
and serve as your slave.

189
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:53,379
Let her atone for all eternity.

190
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:22,580
The time has come.

191
00:10:23,299 --> 00:10:26,659
I'll personally see you off.

192
00:10:47,039 --> 00:10:48,360
[Qi turbulence,]

193
00:10:49,039 --> 00:10:50,120
[meridian entanglement.]

194
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,659
[How could this be?]

195
00:10:59,899 --> 00:11:00,940
It's you!

196
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:06,559
You poisoned my wine!

197
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,299
Protect the Queen!

198
00:11:18,799 --> 00:11:19,759
Quick, protect the Queen!

199
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,320
You...

200
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,899
Are you human or ghost?

201
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,720
Human,

202
00:11:28,899 --> 00:11:30,600
but a ghost that will take your life.

203
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,720
I urge you to purge the court,

204
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,960
and bring peace to the nation.

205
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,399
Do you think I haven't considered it?

206
00:11:41,820 --> 00:11:42,840
But Xie Zhicang

207
00:11:43,559 --> 00:11:44,740
is deeply rooted.

208
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,679
One move could shake the whole.

209
00:11:47,379 --> 00:11:48,919
I must consider the Emperor

210
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,279
and the nation.

211
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:55,639
If so,

212
00:12:03,419 --> 00:12:04,419
I'll have to

213
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:09,100
try another approach.

214
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,200
What do you want?

215
00:12:11,940 --> 00:12:13,159
To convince you.

216
00:12:18,639 --> 00:12:19,980
Anrao would beg you,

217
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:21,740
but I won't.

218
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:23,960
You have two choices:

219
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,039
either

220
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:28,980
cooperate with me to kill Xie Zhicang,

221
00:12:29,899 --> 00:12:30,480
or

222
00:12:32,779 --> 00:12:33,559
die.

223
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:41,059
This painting is so brilliant.

224
00:12:42,179 --> 00:12:43,539
If it spreads among the people,

225
00:12:45,879 --> 00:12:47,740
the Queen Mother can only

226
00:12:49,139 --> 00:12:50,159
choose death as an apology.

227
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:53,399
Even if I agree,

228
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,240
it must be planned carefully.

229
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,620
He is a powerful official.

230
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,039
He can't be killed at will.

231
00:13:00,259 --> 00:13:01,879
If Xie Zhicang is found guilty,

232
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,820
the entire Xie family will be in danger,

233
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:05,879
including Xie Lingfeng.

234
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,379
It's precisely because his martial arts

235
00:13:12,379 --> 00:13:13,440
and power are so formidable

236
00:13:14,299 --> 00:13:16,440
ordinary methods can't deal with him.

237
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,639
Fortunately,

238
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,639
I'm a madman who doesn't care about his life.

239
00:13:23,759 --> 00:13:24,580
That's why

240
00:13:25,100 --> 00:13:27,480
the Queen Mother can get rid of him.

241
00:13:30,539 --> 00:13:32,279
I just need you to do one thing.

242
00:13:32,779 --> 00:13:33,759
At the funeral,

243
00:13:35,179 --> 00:13:37,120
hand him a cup of wine for me.

244
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:42,000
I'll take responsibility

245
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:44,840
for all the blood debts.

246
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:46,679
Xie Zhicang,

247
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,019
today is your day of death!

248
00:13:50,379 --> 00:13:51,500
Do you remember Su Heng,

249
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:53,379
who served you loyally eight years ago?

250
00:13:53,899 --> 00:13:55,059
When you ordered his death,

251
00:13:55,639 --> 00:13:56,580
did you ever imagine

252
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,179
that you would meet the same fate?

253
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,039
Su Heng?

254
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:03,799
He was nothing but an ant!

255
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:06,100
I, Xie Zhicang,

256
00:14:06,820 --> 00:14:09,080
never remember the names of the dead!

257
00:14:10,139 --> 00:14:10,659
Mu Qing,

258
00:14:11,059 --> 00:14:11,620
take the sword.

259
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:14,860
Today,

260
00:14:15,539 --> 00:14:17,539
you'll pay with your life.

261
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,700
Go and

262
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:22,980
kowtow to the ghosts

263
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,279
you wronged.

264
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:24,779
Luo Yao,

265
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,820
if you hurt me,

266
00:14:35,519 --> 00:14:36,779
the Xie Family Army

267
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:40,879
will tear you apart.

268
00:14:41,899 --> 00:14:42,860
Lingfeng,

269
00:14:43,679 --> 00:14:45,000
kill her!

270
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:51,500
Turn your head,

271
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:53,779
don't look!

272
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:09,659
You traitor!

273
00:15:24,379 --> 00:15:27,960
My great cause...

274
00:15:43,139 --> 00:15:44,639
Prince of Lin'an is dead.

275
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:46,720
Brother,

276
00:15:47,759 --> 00:15:48,440
soldiers,

277
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:50,120
did you see that?

278
00:15:51,019 --> 00:15:52,679
I finally killed my enemy

279
00:15:53,659 --> 00:15:55,019
and avenged you all!

280
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,460
The Jiu Yao Faction

281
00:16:14,279 --> 00:16:15,720
assassinated the Prince of Lin'an.

282
00:16:16,639 --> 00:16:17,799
They will be immediately arrested

283
00:16:18,200 --> 00:16:19,179
and executed on a later date

284
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,500
to demonstrate the divine authority!
